high_descs: Move to the stove to the across from the fridge.
Pick up a ladle from the stove.
Move to the end of the counter to the right of you before the fridge.
Place ladle on a plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Move to the lower cabinet closest to the stove.
Open the cabinet and place the plate inside with the ladle and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a ladle in the cabinet closest to the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the stove.
Pick up the ladle to the left of the stove.
Walk to the end of the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the ladle on a plate to the right of the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Walk back around to the stove and look at the cabinet under the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the plate in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Plae a plate with a ladle on it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the stove.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the stove.
Turn right and walk towards the end of the counter.
Place the spoon on the plate that is on the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the counter at the end.
Open the cabinet below the counter and place the plate in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a spoon inside the cabinet.
